sentences.english: Why does the Tetrarch look at me all the while with his mole's eyes under his shaking eyelids?
sentences.chinese: 爲什麼主公一直用賊溜溜的眼睛看着我？

sentences.english: FIRST SOLDIER: Yes; that is Herodias the Tetrarch's wife.
sentences.chinese: 是的，那正是希羅蒂，主公的妻子。

sentences.english: SALOME: I am not tired. Tetrarch.
Master is a toothless old man, grey hair lazily draping over his broad shoulders.
sentences.chinese: 主公是個牙齒全部脫落褐色過肩長髮慵懶披散的老人。

sentences.english: Or maybe longer than that if you can keep your web wound tight around him.
sentences.chinese: 甚至還不止，只要你的羅網把小主公套得更牢一點。

sentences.english: THE SLAVE: Princess the Tetrarch prays you to return to the feast.
sentences.chinese: 公主，主公請你務必要回宴會去。

sentences.english: Any idiot knows zhao yun is not gonna let his zu gong get killed.
sentences.chinese: 任何白癡都知道趙雲不會讓他的主公被殺的。

sentences.english: I think he is afraid of him the Tetrarch.
Often I have heard the Tetrarch talk of him.
sentences.chinese: 我不只一次聽到主公對他的談論。

sentences.english: My lord, invite him to drink wine tomorrow and send him back drunk.
sentences.chinese: 主公明日可請他來喫酒，使盡醉而歸。

sentences.english: The Tetrarch sent him the ring.
